controllers.gui

Class StudyLinks

  • java.lang.Object
    • play.mvc.Results
      • play.mvc.Controller
        • controllers.gui.StudyLinks
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    play.mvc.Http.HeaderNames, play.mvc.Http.Status

    @Singleton
public class StudyLinks
extends play.mvc.Controller
    Controller for all actions regarding study links, batches, and workers within the JATOS GUI.
